Class SpaceObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.SpaceObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Debris, Payload, Satellite, Unknown

    public abstract class SpaceObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a general space object with common attributes such as identification, origin, orbital characteristics, and tracking information.

    This abstract class serves as a base for specific types of space objects, providing shared properties and enforcing the implementation of the getInfo() method.
